Description: nDPI xt_ndpi netfilter module (DKMS source)
 Out-of-tree netfilter kernel module providing the iptables/ip6tables
 "-m ndpi" match, built from the vel21ripn nDPI fork (carries the kernel
 6.8.x fixes). DKMS compiles xt_ndpi against the running kernel on install
 and automatically rebuilds it on every kernel upgrade, so the module keeps
 loading across reboots without manual intervention.
 .
 Note: using the "-m ndpi" match from iptables additionally requires the
 userspace libxt_ndpi.so xtables extension, which is not shipped here.